Finds the perpendicular of a vector in the counter-clockwise direction, such that perp ( right ) = forward, perp ( 1.0, 0.0 ) = ( 0.0, 1.0 ) perp ( forward ) = left, perp ( 0.0, 1.0 ) = ( -1.0, 0.0 ) perp ( left ) = back, perp ( -1.0, 0.0 ) = ( 0.0, -1.0 ) perp ( back ) = right, perp ( 0.0, -1.0 ) = ( 1.0, 0.0 )
